TypeSignature.Value: .class public interface auto ansi abstract ChartObjects implements class System.Collections.IEnumerable

summary.span: 所有的集合指定的图表工作表、 对话框工作表或工作表上的对象。

span.span: A collection of all the objects on the specified chart sheet, dialog sheet, or worksheet.

remarks.span:
每个ChartObject对象代表内嵌的图表。ChartObject对象充当容器对象。ChartObject对象的属性和方法控制的外观和工作表上嵌入图表的大小。使用
方法可返回ChartObjects集合。使用方法可创建一个新的嵌入的图表并将其添加到集合。使用方法，以添加数据并设置其格式的新图表。
使用ChartObjects()，其中是嵌入的图表的索引号或名称，可返回单个ChartObject对象。

span.para: Each ChartObject object represents an embedded chart. The ChartObject object acts as a container for a object. Properties and methods for the ChartObject object control the appearance and size of the embedded chart on the sheet.
Use the method to return the ChartObjects collection. Use the method to create a new, empty embedded chart and add it to the collection. Use the method to add data and format the new chart.
Use ChartObjects(), where is the embedded chart index number or name, to return a single ChartObject object.

MemberSignature.Value: public: property double Left { double get(); void set(double value); };

summary.span: 从对象左边缘到工作表） 的 A 列的左边的缘或 （在图表上） 的图表区的左边的缘的距离。

span.span: The distance from the left edge of the object to the left edge of column A (on a worksheet) or the left edge of the chart area (on a chart).

remarks.span:
如果窗口处于最大化
，此属性返回会有所不同，为负数基于窗口边框的宽度。此属性设置为 0 （零） 将使窗口稍微有点小超过将应用程序窗口已最大化状态。换句话说，如果此属性为 0 （零），Microsoft Excel 主窗口的左边的框将几乎会显示在屏幕上。

span.para: If the window is maximized, this property returns a negative number that varies based on the width of the window border. Setting this property to 0 (zero) will make the window a tiny bit smaller than it would be if the application window were maximized. In other words, if this property is 0 (zero), the left border of the main Microsoft Excel window will just barely be visible on the screen.
